WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:00:20.378 --> 00:00:23.518
In a desperate time...

00:00:25.100 --> 00:00:35.000
when mortal men and women didn't quite know how to make their skis perform...

00:00:38.420 --> 00:00:44.480
They struggled to ski in all terrain and all conditions...

00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:53.620
Leading to an existence plagued with great suffering and frustration...

00:01:06.820 --> 00:01:12.660
But up from the ashes rose intrepid ski instructors...

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:15.080
To give them guidance... 

00:01:18.160 --> 00:01:23.580
leading them on a path to fulfill their dreams...

00:01:31.140 --> 00:01:35.960
Challenging them to lose their minds... 

00:01:36.120 --> 00:01:39.280
And reach technical enlightenment...

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:51.360
With a new instructional video series...

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:59.340
And performance camps around the globe...

00:02:00.300 --> 00:02:03.720
Section 8 Snowsport Institute... 

00:02:03.813 --> 00:02:07.273
Making ordinary skiing...

00:02:08.050 --> 00:02:10.430
Epic!

